Timer reload values: (to wrap each 10ms, or 100 Hz)

xfr123 & 0x0f  |  xfr122 & 0x20

     ||  0x00   0x20  ||
-----><---------------><-------------><
0x00 || 0x3CB0 0xEC78 || 50000 5000      ~ 5 MHz      / 500 kHz
