0x0E || 0xE796 0xFD8F || 6250  625       ~ 625 kHz    / 62.5 kHz
0x0F || 0x7960 0xD8F0 || 34464 10000     ~ 3.4464 MHz / 1 MHz



8051's timer runs at 1/12 rate (usually)

So this means that the 8051 runs at .... 5 * 12 = 60 MHz ?!


